00Z","msg":"大家咪日日喺電視聽嗰隻《珍惜香港 這個家》<br />\n[/url]<a href=\"https://youtu.be/hjBIHV45rrI[url]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FhjBIHV45rrI%5Burl%5D&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRhmaKe8vvTAxx9uYoYxOzRs%3D&h=7e040ec8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/hjBIHV45rrI[url]</a><br />\n聽到頭痛？而家有解决方法嘞。既然政府唔填詞，我就幫佢填咗。以彼之道，還施彼身。唔該幫我廣發推到政府抽起隻嘢！<br />\n<br />\n《真。珍惜香港 這個家》<br />\n<br />\n不必怕，不畏强權下的濫捕<br />\n在我港，望硝煙正高<br />\n在那罪孽滔天的建制内，<br />\n讓這火為我蒼生舞｡<br />\n<br />\n權貴幫，牆外看，把市民當糟糠。不理褒貶，奴性盡現。<br />\n無懼怕，無後退，讓我時代革命！沒作犧牲，别妄想得庇蔭。<br />\n<br />\n(以下重複旋律，如用廣告中嘅短版本，就跳去最後－段&quot;和你飛&quot;結尾)<br />\n<br />\n箭在弦，借問誰曾站起捍衛，<br />\n令政府敗退得徹底。<br />\n願那勇武之獅吼遍天地，<br />\n盡破這惡魔的詭計。<br />\n<br />\n全政開，容自决，這訴求沒法擋。不再出聲，便要絕望。<br />\n和你飛，陪你闖，要自由現我邦。普世之聲，你我一起見證。"},{"pid":"050b5c6427839684b0e50baf47a5f22b706ec2ca","tid":1595008,"uid":9281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T12:36:30.000Z","msg":"加埋警暴"},{"pid":"852b30b2b5db9e3e86e365669d2820c75673c6c3","tid":1595008,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T12:50:52.000Z","msg":"啱 樓主有諗頭"},{"pid":"7bdee3c1e4d6b87214dd0ace6f0c733a0e2533c8","tid":1595008,"uid":9281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T13:26:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3f22186a9fdfd6c3b6646f1bb1106c32444a3c0","tid":1595008,"uid":71092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T14:49:44.000Z","msg":"應該要！"},{"pid":"afe6dd7f4f43aeb88be31f99cd9476a4a181c144","tid":1595008,"uid":9281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T15:32:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}